## Installation

### Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/AdvancedPasswordGenerator.git
```

### Navigate to the project

```bash
cd AdvancedPasswordGenerator
```

### Compile

```bash
javac AdvancedPasswordGenerator.java
```

### Run

```bash
